<lb n="0070c08" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="1" type="卷"/><cb:jhead>佛說優填王經</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0070c09" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0070c10" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator">西晉<note n="0070003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔沙門〕－【宋】【宮】</note><note n="0070003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">沙門【大】，〔－〕【宋】【宮】</note><app n="0070003"><lem wit="【大】">沙門</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>釋法炬<note n="0070004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔奉詔〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0070004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">奉詔【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0070004"><lem wit="【大】">奉　詔</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>譯</byline>
<lb n="0070c11" ed="T"/><cb:div type="jing"><p xml:id="pT12p0070c1101">聞如是：</p><p xml:id="pT12p0070c1104" rend="inline">一時佛在拘深國，<note n="0070005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（國）＋王【三】【宮】</note><note n="0070005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">王【大】，國王【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0070005"><lem wit="【大】">王</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">國王</rdg></app>號曰優填。拘
<lb n="0070c12" ed="T"/>深國有逝心，名摩<note n="0070006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">回＝因【元】【明】【宮】</note><note n="0070006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">回【大】，因【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0070006"><lem wit="【大】">回</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】【宮】">因</rdg></app>提，生女端正華色世間
<lb n="0070c13" ed="T"/>少雙。父覩女容一國希有，名曰無比。鄰國諸
<lb n="0070c14" ed="T"/>王群<note n="0070007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">僚＝寮【三】【宮】</note><note n="0070007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">僚【大】，寮【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0070007"><lem wit="【大】">僚</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">寮</rdg></app>豪姓靡不娉焉。父答曰：「若有君子
<lb n="0070c15" ed="T"/>容與女齊，吾其應之。」</p><p xml:id="pT12p0070c1509" rend="inline">佛時行在其國，逝心
<lb n="0070c16" ed="T"/>覩佛三十二相八十種好，身色紫金巍巍堂
<lb n="0070c17" ed="T"/>堂光儀無上，心喜而曰：「吾女獲匹。」歸語其妻
<lb n="0070c18" ed="T"/>曰：「吾為無比得婿。」促莊飾女將往也。夫妻
<lb n="0070c19" ed="T"/>共服飾，其女步<note n="0070008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">瑤＝搖【三】【宮】</note><note n="0070008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">瑤【大】，搖【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0070008"><lem wit="【大】">瑤</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">搖</rdg></app>華光，珠璣瓔珞莊<note n="0070009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">嚴＝飾【三】【宮】</note><note n="0070009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">嚴【大】，飾【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0070009"><lem wit="【大】">嚴</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">飾</rdg></app>光
<lb n="0070c20" ed="T"/>國，夫妻共將女至佛所。妻道見佛迹相好之
<lb n="0070c21" ed="T"/>文光<note n="0070010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">彩＝綵【宋】【宮】</note><note n="0070010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">彩【大】，綵【宋】【宮】</note><app n="0070010"><lem wit="【大】">彩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">綵</rdg></app>之色，非世所有，知為天尊，謂其夫
<lb n="0070c22" ed="T"/>曰：「此人足跡文理乃爾，非世所聞斯將非凡，
<lb n="0070c23" ed="T"/>必自清淨無復婬欲，將不取吾女，無自辱也。」
<lb n="0070c24" ed="T"/>夫曰：「何以知其然？」妻因說偈言：</p>
<lb n="0070c25" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT12p0070c2501" rend="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em"><l>「婬人曳踵行，</l><l>恚者<note n="0070011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">操＝歛【元】【明】</note><note n="0070011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">操【大】，歛【元】【明】</note><app n="0070011"><lem wit="【大】">操</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">歛</rdg></app>指步，</l>
<lb n="0070c26" ed="T"/><l>愚者足<note n="0070012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">躘＝蹴【元】【明】</note><note n="0070012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">躘【大】，蹴【元】【明】</note><app n="0070012"><lem wit="【大】">躘</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">蹴</rdg></app>地；</l><l>斯跡天人尊。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0070c27" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT12p0070c2701">逝心曰：「非爾女人所知，汝不樂者<note n="0070013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">便＋（自）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0070013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">便【大】，便自【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0070013"><lem wit="【大】">便</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">便自</rdg></app>還歸。」
<lb n="0070c28" ed="T"/>乃自將女<note n="0070014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（往）＋詣【三】【宮】</note><note n="0070014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">詣【大】，往詣【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0070014"><lem wit="【大】">詣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">往詣</rdg></app>佛所，稽首佛足，白佛言：「大人
<lb n="0070c29" ed="T"/>勤勞教授，身無供養。有是麁女，願給箕<g ref="#CB00416"/>。」</p><p xml:id="pT12p0070c2917" rend="inline">佛
<pb n="0071a" xml:id="T12.0332.0071a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0071a01" ed="T"/>言：「汝以女為好耶？」</p><p xml:id="pT12p0071a0108" rend="inline">答曰：「生得此女顏容實
<lb n="0071a02" ed="T"/>好世間無雙，諸國王豪姓多有求者不以應
<lb n="0071a03" ed="T"/>之。竊見大人光色巍巍非世所見，貪得供養
<lb n="0071a04" ed="T"/>故，宜自歸耳。」</p><p xml:id="pT12p0071a0406" rend="inline">佛言：「此女之好為著何許？」</p><p xml:id="pT12p0071a0416" rend="inline">逝心
<lb n="0071a05" ed="T"/>曰：「從頭至足周遍觀之無不好也。」</p><p xml:id="pT12p0071a0514" rend="inline">佛言：「惑哉
<lb n="0071a06" ed="T"/>肉眼，吾觀之，從頭至足無一好耶。若頭上有
<lb n="0071a07" ed="T"/>髮，但是毛象馬之尾亦皆爾也；髮下有髑髏，
<lb n="0071a08" ed="T"/>但是骨屠家猪頭骨亦爾也；頭中有腦者如
<lb n="0071a09" ed="T"/>泥<note n="0071001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鯹＝腥【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0071001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鯹【大】＊，腥【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0071001"><lem wit="【大】">鯹</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">腥</rdg></app>臊<note n="0071002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">送＝逆【三】【宮】</note><note n="0071002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">送【大】，逆【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0071002"><lem wit="【大】">送</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">逆</rdg></app>，鼻下之著地莫能蹈者，目者是
<lb n="0071a10" ed="T"/><note n="0071003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">脆＝胞【三】【宮】</note><note n="0071003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">脆【大】，胞【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0071003"><lem wit="【大】">脆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">胞</rdg></app>決之純汁，鼻中有涕，口但有唾，腹藏肝
<lb n="0071a11" ed="T"/>肺皆亦<app type="star" corresp="#0071001"><lem wit="【大】">鯹</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">腥</rdg></app>臊，腸胃膀胱但成屎尿腐臭難論，
<lb n="0071a12" ed="T"/>腹為<note n="0071004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">幃＝韋【元】【明】</note><note n="0071004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">幃【大】，韋【元】【明】</note><app n="0071004"><lem wit="【大】">幃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">韋</rdg></app>囊裹諸不淨，四支手足骨骨相<note n="0071005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">拄＝柱【宋】【宮】</note><note n="0071005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">拄【大】，柱【宋】【宮】</note><app n="0071005"><lem wit="【大】">拄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">柱</rdg></app>筋
<lb n="0071a13" ed="T"/>連皮<note n="0071a1301" resp="CBETA" type="add">韜【CB】【麗-CB】，鞱【大】</note><app n="0071a1301"><lem wit="【CB】【麗-CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">韜<note type="cf1">K06n0038_p1189b19</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">鞱</rdg></app>，但恃氣息以動作之，譬若木人機關
<lb n="0071a14" ed="T"/>作之，既畢解<note n="0071006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">列＝剝【三】【宮】</note><note n="0071006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">列【大】，剝【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0071006"><lem wit="【大】">列</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">剝</rdg></app>其體節節，相離手足狼<note n="0071007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">藉＝籍【宋】【元】【宮】</note><note n="0071007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">藉【大】，籍【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0071007"><lem wit="【大】">藉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">籍</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0071a15" ed="T"/>人亦如是，有何等好而云少雙？昔者吾在貝
<lb n="0071a16" ed="T"/>多樹下，第六魔天王莊飾三女，顏容華色天
<lb n="0071a17" ed="T"/>中無比非徒此<note n="0071008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">論＝倫【三】【宮】</note><note n="0071008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">論【大】，倫【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0071008"><lem wit="【大】">論</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">倫</rdg></app>，欲以壞吾道意，我為說
<lb n="0071a18" ed="T"/>身中穢惡，即皆化成老母形壞不復，慚愧而
<lb n="0071a19" ed="T"/>去。今是屎囊欲何所戀？急將還去，吾不取也。」</p>
<lb n="0071a20" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT12p0071a2001">逝心聞佛所說，忽然慚恥無辭復言，又白佛
<lb n="0071a21" ed="T"/>言：「若仁不取者，更以妻優填王可乎不？」佛不
<lb n="0071a22" ed="T"/>答焉。逝心即送女與優填王，王獲女大悅，拜
<lb n="0071a23" ed="T"/>父為太傅，為女<note n="0071009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">興＝與【三】【宮】</note><note n="0071009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">興【大】，與【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0071009"><lem wit="【大】">興</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">與</rdg></app>宮，伎樂千人以給侍之。
<lb n="0071a24" ed="T"/>王正后師事佛，得須陀洹道。此女<note n="0071a2401" resp="CBETA" type="add">譖【CB】【麗-CB】，讚【大】</note><app n="0071a2401"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】【麗-CB】">譖<note type="cf1">K06n0038_p1189c09</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">讚</rdg></app>之於王，
<lb n="0071a25" ed="T"/>王惑其言以百箭射其后。后見箭不懼，都無
<lb n="0071a26" ed="T"/>恚怒，一意念佛慈心長跪向王，箭皆繞后
<lb n="0071a27" ed="T"/>三匝還住王前，百箭皆爾。王乃自驚<note n="0071010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">暢＝悵【三】【宮】</note><note n="0071010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">暢【大】，悵【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0071010"><lem wit="【大】">暢</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">悵</rdg></app>然
<lb n="0071a28" ed="T"/>而懼，即駕白<note n="0071011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">象＝像【宮】</note><note n="0071011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">象【大】，像【宮】</note><app n="0071011"><lem wit="【大】">象</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">像</rdg></app>金車馳詣佛所，未到下車
<lb n="0071a29" ed="T"/><note n="0071012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">避＝僻【宋】【宮】，辟【元】【明】</note><note n="0071012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">避【大】，僻【宋】【宮】，辟【元】【明】</note><app n="0071012"><lem wit="【大】">避</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">僻</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">辟</rdg></app><note n="0071013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">從＝徒【宮】</note><note n="0071013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">從【大】，徒【宮】</note><app n="0071013"><lem wit="【大】">從</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">徒</rdg></app>步進稽首佛足，長跪自陳曰：「吾有重
<pb n="0071b" xml:id="T12.0332.0071b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0071b01" ed="T"/>咎在三尊，所以彼婬妖<note n="0071014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">從＝縱【明】【宮】</note><note n="0071014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">從【大】，縱【明】【宮】</note><app n="0071014"><lem wit="【大】">從</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【宮】">縱</rdg></app>欲興邪，於佛聖
<lb n="0071b02" ed="T"/>眾每一惡念，以箭百<note n="0071015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">枚＝放【宮】</note><note n="0071015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">枚【大】，放【宮】</note><app n="0071015"><lem wit="【大】">枚</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">放</rdg></app>射佛弟子，如事陳
<lb n="0071b03" ed="T"/>之覩之心懼，<note n="0071016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">唯＝惟【宮】＊</note><note n="0071016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">唯【大】＊，惟【宮】＊</note><app n="0071016"><lem wit="【大】">唯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">惟</rdg></app>佛至真無量之慈，白衣弟
<lb n="0071b04" ed="T"/>子慈力乃爾，豈況無上正真佛乎？我今首過
<lb n="0071b05" ed="T"/>歸命三尊，<app type="star" corresp="#0071016"><lem wit="【大】">唯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">惟</rdg></app>佛弘慈原赦其咎。」</p><p xml:id="pT12p0071b0513" rend="inline">佛笑曰：
<lb n="0071b06" ed="T"/>「善哉王！覺惡悔過，此明人行也，吾受王善意。」</p>
<lb n="0071b07" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT12p0071b0701">王稽首，如是至三，佛亦三受之。王又頭面著
<lb n="0071b08" ed="T"/>地，退就坐曰：「稟氣<note n="0071017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">匈＝凶【三】【宮】</note><note n="0071017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">匈【大】，凶【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0071017"><lem wit="【大】">匈</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">凶</rdg></app>頑忿戾自恣無忍辱心，
<lb n="0071b09" ed="T"/>三毒不除惡行快意，順女妖邪不知其惡，自
<lb n="0071b10" ed="T"/>惟壽終必入地獄，願佛加哀，廣說女惡魑魅
<lb n="0071b11" ed="T"/>之態，入其羅網尠能自拔，吾聞其禍必以
<lb n="0071b12" ed="T"/>自<note n="0071018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">誡＝戒【三】【宮】</note><note n="0071018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">誡【大】，戒【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0071018"><lem wit="【大】">誡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">戒</rdg></app>，國民巨細得以改操。」</p><p xml:id="pT12p0071b1211" rend="inline">佛言：「用此<note n="0071019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">問為且＝為問且【宋】【元】，為問具【明】</note><note n="0071019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">問為且【大】，為問且【宋】【元】，為問具【明】</note><app n="0071019"><lem wit="【大】">問
<lb n="0071b13" ed="T"/>為？且</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">為問且</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">為問具</rdg></app>說餘義。」</p><p xml:id="pT12p0071b1306" rend="inline">王曰：「餘事異日說之不<note n="0071020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">晚＝免【宮】</note><note n="0071020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">晚【大】，免【宮】</note><app n="0071020"><lem wit="【大】">晚</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">免</rdg></app>，女
<lb n="0071b14" ed="T"/>亂惑意<note n="0071021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">兇＝凶【宮】</note><note n="0071021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">兇【大】，凶【宮】</note><app n="0071021"><lem wit="【大】">兇</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">凶</rdg></app>禍之大，不聞其禍何緣遠之？願
<lb n="0071b15" ed="T"/>佛具為吾釋地獄之變及女人之穢。」</p><p xml:id="pT12p0071b1515" rend="inline">佛言：「具
<lb n="0071b16" ed="T"/>聽！男子有<note n="0071022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">淫＝媱【三】【宮】下同</note><note n="0071022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">淫【大】下同，媱【宋】【元】【明】【宮】下同</note><app n="0071022"><lem wit="【大】">淫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">媱</rdg></app>之惡，却覩女妖。」</p><p xml:id="pT12p0071b1612" rend="inline">王曰：「善願受
<lb n="0071b17" ed="T"/>明教。」</p><p xml:id="pT12p0071b1703" rend="inline">佛言：「具聽！男子有四惡，急所當知。世有
<lb n="0071b18" ed="T"/>婬夫，恒想覩女思聞妖聲，遠捨正法疑真信
<lb n="0071b19" ed="T"/>邪，<note n="0071023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">婬＝邪【宮】</note><note n="0071023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">婬【大】，邪【宮】</note><app n="0071023"><lem wit="【大】">婬</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">邪</rdg></app>網所<note n="0071024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">綶＝纏【三】【宮】</note><note n="0071024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">綶【大】，纏【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0071024"><lem wit="【大】">綶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">纏</rdg></app>沒在盲冥，為欲所使如奴畏
<lb n="0071b20" ed="T"/>主；貪樂女色，不覺九孔惡露之臭穢，渾沌欲
<lb n="0071b21" ed="T"/>中，如猪處溷不覺其臭快以為安，不計後當
<lb n="0071b22" ed="T"/>在無<note n="0071025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">澤＝擇【三】【宮】</note><note n="0071025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">澤【大】，擇【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0071025"><lem wit="【大】">澤</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">擇</rdg></app>之獄受痛無極；注心在淫，<note n="0071026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">噉＝妷【宋】【宮】，泆【元】【明】</note><note n="0071026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">噉【大】，妷【宋】【宮】，泆【元】【明】</note><app n="0071026"><lem wit="【大】">噉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">妷</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">泆</rdg></app>其涕
<lb n="0071b23" ed="T"/>唾翫其膿血，珍之如玉甘之如蜜；故曰欲態
<lb n="0071b24" ed="T"/>之士。此為一惡態也。又親之養子懷妊生育，
<lb n="0071b25" ed="T"/>稚得長大勤苦難論，到子成人<note n="0071027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">𢣷＝擢【三】【宮】</note><note n="0071027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">懼【大】，擢【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0071027"><lem wit="【大】">懼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">擢</rdg></app>家竭財膝
<lb n="0071b26" ed="T"/>行肘步，因媒表情致彼為妻，若在異域尋而
<lb n="0071b27" ed="T"/>追之，不問遠近不避勤苦，注意在婬捐忘親
<lb n="0071b28" ed="T"/>老，既得為妻貴之如寶，欲私相娛樂惡見父
<lb n="0071b29" ed="T"/>母，信其妖言或致鬪訟，不惟身所從生<note n="0071028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">孤＝辜【三】【宮】</note><note n="0071028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">孤【大】，辜【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0071028"><lem wit="【大】">孤</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">辜</rdg></app>
<pb n="0071c" xml:id="T12.0332.0071c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0071c01" ed="T"/>親無量之恩。斯謂二惡態也。又人處世勤
<lb n="0071c02" ed="T"/>苦疲勞躬自致財，本<note n="0071029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">自＝有【宮】</note><note n="0071029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">自【大】，有【宮】</note><app n="0071029"><lem wit="【大】">自</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">有</rdg></app>誠信敬道之意，尊戴
<lb n="0071c03" ed="T"/>沙門梵志之心，覺世非常，布施為福。取妻之
<lb n="0071c04" ed="T"/>後，情惑婬欲愚蔽自擁，背真向邪專由女
<lb n="0071c05" ed="T"/><note n="0071030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">色＝衒【宮】</note><note n="0071030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">色【大】，衒【宮】</note><app n="0071030"><lem wit="【大】">色</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">衒</rdg></app>，若有布施之意，雖欲發言相呼女色，
<lb n="0071c06" ed="T"/>絕清淨行更成小人，不識佛經之<note n="0071031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">戒＝重誡【三】【宮】</note><note n="0071031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">戒【大】，重誡【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0071031"><lem wit="【大】">戒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">重誡</rdg></app>禍福之
<lb n="0071c07" ed="T"/>歸，苟為婬色投身羅網，必墮惡道終而不改。
<lb n="0071c08" ed="T"/>斯謂三惡態也。又為人子不惟養恩，治生致
<lb n="0071c09" ed="T"/>財不以養親，但以東西廣求婬路，懷持寶物
<lb n="0071c10" ed="T"/>招人婦女，或殺六畜婬祀鬼神，飲酒歌舞合
<lb n="0071c11" ed="T"/>會之後，<note n="0071032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">至＝亙【三】【宮】</note><note n="0071032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">至【大】，亙【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0071032"><lem wit="【大】">至</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">亙</rdg></app>求方便更相招呼，以遂<note n="0071033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">奸＝姦【宮】</note><note n="0071033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">奸【大】，姦【宮】</note><app n="0071033"><lem wit="【大】">奸</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">姦</rdg></app>情，
<lb n="0071c12" ed="T"/>及其獲偶喜無以喻，婬結縛著無所復識。當
<lb n="0071c13" ed="T"/>爾之時<app type="star" corresp="#0071016"><lem wit="【大】">唯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">惟</rdg></app>此為樂，不覺惡露之臭穢地獄之
<lb n="0071c14" ed="T"/>苦痛，一則可笑二則可畏，譬若狂<note n="0071034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">犬＝笑【三】【宮】</note><note n="0071034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">犬【大】，笑【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0071034"><lem wit="【大】">犬</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">笑</rdg></app>不知
<lb n="0071c15" ed="T"/>其非。斯謂四惡態也。」佛言：「男子有是四惡，用
<lb n="0071c16" ed="T"/>墮三塗，當審遠此<note n="0071035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">態＝能【三】【宮】</note><note n="0071035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">態【大】，能【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0071035"><lem wit="【大】">態</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">能</rdg></app>免苦耳。復聽說女人之
<lb n="0071c17" ed="T"/>惡。」佛便說偈言：</p>
<lb n="0071c18" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT12p0071c1801" rend="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em"><l>「已為欲所使，</l><l>放意不能安，</l>
<lb n="0071c19" ed="T"/><l>習施於非法，</l><l>將何以為賢？</l>
<lb n="0071c20" ed="T"/><l>欲為畜生行，</l><l>以<note n="0071036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">欲＝為【明】</note><note n="0071036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">欲【大】，為【明】</note><app n="0071036"><lem wit="【大】">欲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">為</rdg></app>還自殃，</l>
<lb n="0071c21" ed="T"/><l>溷虫在臭中，</l><l>不知為處難。</l>
<lb n="0071c22" ed="T"/><l>如虫在冥中，</l><l>不知東以西，</l>
<lb n="0071c23" ed="T"/><l>結著於婬欲，</l><l>惡此亦虫論。</l>
<lb n="0071c24" ed="T"/><l>婬既不見道，</l><l>日夜種罪根，</l>
<lb n="0071c25" ed="T"/><l>現世君臣亂，</l><l>上下為迷昏，</l>
<lb n="0071c26" ed="T"/><l>王法為錯亂，</l><l>正法為迷<note n="0071037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">樊＝焚【元】【明】【宮】</note><note n="0071037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">樊【大】，焚【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0071037"><lem wit="【大】">樊</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】【宮】">焚</rdg></app>，</l>
<lb n="0071c27" ed="T"/><l>農夫捨常業，</l><l>賈人為<note n="0071038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">珍＝彌【宮】</note><note n="0071038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">珍【大】，彌【宮】</note><app n="0071038"><lem wit="【大】">珍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">彌</rdg></app>連。</l>
<lb n="0071c28" ed="T"/><l>現世更牢獄，</l><l>死復入太山，</l>
<lb n="0071c29" ed="T"/><l>當受百種毒，</l><l>其痛難可<note n="0071039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">當＝言【明】【宮】</note><note n="0071039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">當【大】，言【明】【宮】</note><app n="0071039"><lem wit="【大】">當</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【宮】">言</rdg></app>。</l>
<pb n="0072a" xml:id="T12.0332.0072a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0072a01" ed="T"/><l>洋銅灌其口，</l><l>山<note n="0072001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">連＝車【元】【明】</note><note n="0072001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">連【大】，車【元】【明】</note><app n="0072001"><lem wit="【大】">連</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">車</rdg></app>笮其身，</l>
<lb n="0072a02" ed="T"/><l>此輩有百數，</l><l>難可一一陳。</l>
<lb n="0072a03" ed="T"/><l>常在三惡道，</l><l>宛轉如車輪，</l>
<lb n="0072a04" ed="T"/><l>若世時有佛，</l><l>而已不得聞。</l>
<lb n="0072a05" ed="T"/><l>女人最為惡，</l><l>難與為因緣，</l>
<lb n="0072a06" ed="T"/><l>恩愛一縛著，</l><l>牽人入罪門。</l>
<lb n="0072a07" ed="T"/><l>女人<note n="0072002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">為何＝何為【三】【宮】</note><note n="0072002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">為何【大】，何為【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0072002"><lem wit="【大】">為何</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">何為</rdg></app>好？</l><l>但是屎尿囊，</l>
<lb n="0072a08" ed="T"/><l>何不諦係視，</l><l>為此而狂荒？</l>
<lb n="0072a09" ed="T"/><l>其內甚臭穢，</l><l>外為嚴飾容，</l>
<lb n="0072a10" ed="T"/><l>家有含毒蝎，</l><l>劇如蛇以龍。</l>
<lb n="0072a11" ed="T"/><l>譬<note n="0072003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">如＝若【三】【宮】</note><note n="0072003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">如【大】，若【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0072003"><lem wit="【大】">如</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">若</rdg></app>錦韜<note n="0072004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">牟＝矛【元】【明】</note><note n="0072004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">牟【大】，矛【元】【明】</note><app n="0072004"><lem wit="【大】">牟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">矛</rdg></app>，</l><l>羅縠<note n="0072005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">綶＝裏【三】【宮】</note><note n="0072005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">綶【大】，裏【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0072005"><lem wit="【大】">綶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">裏</rdg></app>鋒鋩，</l>
<lb n="0072a12" ed="T"/><l>愚者覩其表，</l><l>翫之以自殃。</l>
<lb n="0072a13" ed="T"/><l>智者覺而捨，</l><l>癡者致死傷，</l>
<lb n="0072a14" ed="T"/><l>婬欲亦如是，</l><l>抱刃以自喪。</l>
<lb n="0072a15" ed="T"/><l>覩新即厭故，</l><l>所樂亦無常，</l>
<lb n="0072a16" ed="T"/><l>言為刀斧截，</l><l>笑為<note n="0072006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">棘以荊＝荊以棘【三】【宮】</note><note n="0072006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">棘以荊【大】，荊以棘【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0072006"><lem wit="【大】">棘以荊</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">荊以棘</rdg></app>。</l>
<lb n="0072a17" ed="T"/><l>內懷臭穢毒，</l><l>飾外以華香，</l>
<lb n="0072a18" ed="T"/><l>癡人貪其味，</l><l>不惟後受殃。</l>
<lb n="0072a19" ed="T"/><l>譬<note n="0072007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">若＝如【明】</note><note n="0072007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">若【大】，如【明】</note><app n="0072007"><lem wit="【大】">若</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">如</rdg></app><note n="0072008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鴆＝沈【宮】</note><note n="0072008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鴆【大】，沈【宮】</note><app n="0072008"><lem wit="【大】">鴆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">沈</rdg></app>毒藥，</l><l>以和甘露漿，</l>
<lb n="0072a20" ed="T"/><l>所向無不壞，</l><l>飲之皆仆僵。</l>
<lb n="0072a21" ed="T"/><l>亦如薪得火，</l><l>草木被重霜，</l>
<lb n="0072a22" ed="T"/><l>覩表不計裏，</l><l>是為最非<note n="0072009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">詳＝祥【三】【宮】</note><note n="0072009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">詳【大】，祥【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0072009"><lem wit="【大】">詳</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">祥</rdg></app>。</l>
<lb n="0072a23" ed="T"/><l>女毒甚於是，</l><l>草乃見形傷，</l>
<lb n="0072a24" ed="T"/><l>絕欲以求道，</l><l>故有婬欲情。</l>
<lb n="0072a25" ed="T"/><l>其形甚易見，</l><l>癡人情不絕，</l>
<lb n="0072a26" ed="T"/><l>羅網四面張，</l><l>去道如絲髮。</l>
<lb n="0072a27" ed="T"/><l>人本清淨種，</l><l>如魚處深淵，</l>
<lb n="0072a28" ed="T"/><l>智者乃自覺，</l><l>著網不得還。</l>
<lb n="0072a29" ed="T"/><l>欲網甚於是，</l><l>結縛甚欲堅，</l>
<pb n="0072b" xml:id="T12.0332.0072b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0072b01" ed="T"/><l>投身<note n="0072010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">置＝<g ref="#CB00155"/>【三】【宮】</note><note n="0072010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">置【大】，<g ref="#CB00155"/>【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0072010"><lem wit="【大】">置</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><g ref="#CB00155"/></rdg></app>荊棘，</l><l>可得脫其身。</l>
<lb n="0072b02" ed="T"/><l>譬若飢猿猴，</l><l>望見熟甘果，</l>
<lb n="0072b03" ed="T"/><l>專心投色欲，</l><l>是輩百向墮。</l>
<lb n="0072b04" ed="T"/><l>亦如魚食鉤，</l><l>飛蛾入燈火，</l>
<lb n="0072b05" ed="T"/><l>愚者見歡喜，</l><l>不<note n="0072011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惟＝遣【宋】</note><note n="0072011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">惟【大】，遣【宋】</note><app n="0072011"><lem wit="【大】">惟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">遣</rdg></app>後受禍。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0072b06" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT12p0072b0601">佛說如是，優填王歡喜，即以頭面著地，白佛
<lb n="0072b07" ed="T"/>言：「實從生<note n="0072012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以＝已【三】【宮】</note><note n="0072012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以【大】，已【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0072012"><lem wit="【大】">以</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">已</rdg></app>來不聞女人之惡乃爾，男子
<lb n="0072b08" ed="T"/><note n="0072013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">悖＝勃【三】【宮】</note><note n="0072013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">悖【大】，勃【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0072013"><lem wit="【大】">悖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">勃</rdg></app>亂隨之墮罪，但不知故不<note n="0072014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">制＝斷【三】【宮】</note><note n="0072014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">制【大】，斷【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0072014"><lem wit="【大】">制</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">斷</rdg></app>心意。從今
<lb n="0072b09" ed="T"/>已後終身自悔，歸命三尊不敢復犯。」為佛作
<lb n="0072b10" ed="T"/>禮，歡喜而去。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0072b11" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead>佛說優填王經</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
</body></text></TEI>